<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.3">
<l>māṉeynōk kiyartam vayiṟṟukkuḻi yiluḻaikkum</l>
<l>ūṉēyāk kaitaṉṉai yutavāmaiyu ṇarntuṇarntu</l>
<l>vāṉēmā nilamē vantuvanteṉma ṉattirunta</l>
<l>tēṉēniṉ ṉaṭaintēṉ tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having pondered and pondered the pointlessness of this body of flesh</l>
<l>For which the pits of the wombs of deer-eyed women labor,</l>
<l rend="indent">[You who is] the great earth [and] the sky,</l>
<l>Nectar which remains in my mind, having come joyfully,</l>
<l>I take refuge in you, the one who dwells in Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
